LibraryAPI/
├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py      # Initializes the Flask app
│   ├── routes.py        # All the API routes
│   ├── models.py        # Book model and data structure
│   └── utils.py         # Helper functions (e.g., validation)
├── .github/workflows/  # For GitHub Actions CI/CD workflows
├── Dockerfile           # Docker instructions for containerization
├── docker-compose.yml   # To manage multiple containers (if needed)
├── README.md            # Instructions on how to run the project
└── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies (Flask, Swagger, etc.)
